Dictionary data (built locally, not committed to this repository)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
The Finnish→English dictionary used by the reading mode is built from the
Wiktionary extract published at https://kaikki.org/dictionary/Finnish/
(Tatu Ylonen: "Wiktextract: Wiktionary as Machine-Readable Structured Data").

Wiktionary content is dual-licensed under CC BY-SA 4.0 and GFDL:
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/
The dictionary database you build with backend/scripts/build_dictionary.py is
therefore CC BY-SA and credited to Wiktionary contributors.

Morphology
----------
Voikko (libvoikko + the Finnish morphological dictionary) is used as an
external dependency (GPL/LGPL/MPL licensed); it is not bundled in this
repository. See https://voikko.puimula.org/.

Content
-------
YLE (Selkouutiset) article text is never stored or committed. The app keeps
only links plus locally generated exercises. Each user supplies their own YLE
API key (https://developer.yle.fi/).

Models
------
Qwen model weights are pulled by the user via Ollama and carry their own
license; they are not part of this repository.
